{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a premium responsive Shopify product listing section with a modern clean aesthetic inspired by high-end D2C snack brands and the same interaction style as the custom reel section we created earlier.
    
    SECTION LAYOUT:
    
    * Full width section touching both left and right edges of the screen
    * Background color: deep crimson red (#D52528)
    * Smooth horizontal draggable product slider/carousel
    * Show 5 product cards at a time on desktop
    * Additional cards continue horizontally with drag/swipe interaction
    * Add smooth snapping effect while dragging
    * Add navigation dots centered at the bottom
    * Maintain equal spacing and clean alignment
    * Entire section should feel modern, premium, responsive, and minimal
    
    PRODUCT CARD DESIGN:
    
    * Clean rounded card with subtle shadow
    * Card background should contrast nicely with crimson background
    * Product image placed at the top with proper padding
    * Large image area with clean spacing
    * Below image add enough dedicated space for long product titles
    * Product title should never feel cramped
    * Add noticeable spacing between:
    
      * Image and title
      * Title and pricing section
    * Price hierarchy:
    
      * Original price smaller and strikethrough
      * Discounted price larger and bold
    * Beside pricing add a rounded red discount badge
    * Inside badge show white text like:
    
      * “20% OFF”
      * “35% OFF”
    * Badge should feel modern and premium
    
    BUTTON DESIGN:
    
    * “View Product” button should be positioned at the bottom edge of the card
    * Half of the button should overlap outside the product card
    * Button should feel floating and modern
    * Rounded pill style
    * Smooth hover animation
    * Premium clean typography
    * Ensure button never gets cut off
    
    RESPONSIVENESS:
    DESKTOP:
    
    * 5 cards visible in one row
    * Horizontal drag/swipe enabled
    * Adjustable card width controls in Shopify customizer
    
    MOBILE:
    
    * Show 4 products total initially
    * 2 cards per row
    * 2 rows layout
    * At bottom add a centered “More” button
    * Clicking More reveals remaining products
    * Cards optimized for mobile spacing
    * No cropped buttons or cut content
    * Maintain premium look on small screens
    
    SHOPIFY CUSTOMIZATION OPTIONS:
    Add customizable settings inside Shopify theme editor for:
    
    * Desktop card width
    * Mobile card width
    * Card border radius
    * Section padding top/bottom
    * Product image ratio
    * Button color
    * Button text
    * Background color
    * Products per row desktop
    * Products per row mobile
    * Discount badge color
    * Enable/disable dots
    * Enable/disable drag interaction
    
    FUNCTIONALITY:
    
    * Smooth draggable/swipe carousel
    * Mouse drag on desktop
    * Touch swipe on mobile
    * Smooth transitions
    * Responsive resizing
    * Lazy loading for images
    * Maintain performance optimization
    
    STYLE REFERENCE:
    
    * Minimal premium Shopify section
    * Clean spacing
    * Gen Z D2C aesthetic
    * Modern floating elements
    * Smooth UI
    * Similar interaction feel to premium snack/fashion Shopify stores
    * No clutter
    * Strong typography hierarchy
    * Premium responsive behavior
